---

<Layout {metadata}>
  <div class="min-h-screen bg-[#F5F1E3] text-[#2C3639] overflow-x-hidden font-pixel">
    <canvas id="matrixCanvas" class="fixed inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-10"></canvas>

